            bad: { user: "They're in a better place now. At least they're not suffering anymore.", ai: "*(winces)* I know you mean well. But I don't want a silver lining right now. I just want my mom back.", note: "\u274c Tried to reframe their pain. They felt dismissed, not comforted." },
            good: { user: "I don't know what to say. I just know I love you and I'm here.", ai: "*(tears)* That's enough. That's actually enough.", note: "\u2713 Didn't try to fix it. Just showed up. That's what grief needs." },
