            good: { user: "Whatever you need right now \u2014 talking, silence, distraction, crying \u2014 I'm here for all of it.", ai: "*(relieved)* Can we just sit here? I don't want to talk yet. I just don't want to be alone.", note: "\u2713 Let them choose. They chose your presence. That's everything." },
