            good: { user: "I know it's been two months. I'm not checking in because I think you should be 'better.' I'm checking in because I know this is when it gets hardest.", ai: "*(breaks down)* Thank you. Everyone else stopped calling. I thought I was supposed to be okay by now.", note: "\u2713 Showed up in the long tail of grief. That's the call that saves someone." },
