            bad: { user: "You've been so checked out. I feel like I'm living with a roommate.", ai: "*(defensive)* I've been exhausted. Sorry I'm not performing enough for you.", note: "\u274c Accused them. Now they're defending instead of connecting." },
            good: { user: "I miss you. Not in a dramatic way. I just feel like somewhere in the chaos of everything, we lost our thread. And I want to find it again.", ai: "*(softens)* I miss you too. I didn't know how to say it.", note: "\u2713 Named the loss as shared. They feel longing, not blame." },
