            good: { user: "What if we started with something tiny? Like sitting together for ten minutes after the kids are asleep. No phones. No agenda. Just us.", ai: "*(exhales)* Ten minutes? Yeah. I can do ten minutes.", note: "\u2713 Small enough to say yes to. That's where reconnection starts." },
