            bad: { user: "I know it's been hard. Hopefully we can get back to normal soon.", ai: "*(flat)* I don't even remember what normal was.", note: "\u274c Dismissed the season as something to get past. They feel unseen in their sacrifice." },
            good: { user: "Before we talk about what's next \u2014 I want to say something. You carried so much through this. I don't think I've told you that. I see what you did for this family and I'm grateful.", ai: "*(tearful)* I didn't think you noticed.", note: "\u2713 Acknowledged the invisible labor. That's the bridge back to each other." },
