            good: { user: "I noticed you laughing from across the room and thought \u2014 that's someone I'd like to talk to. I'm [name].", ai: "*(genuinely smiles)* That's the nicest thing anyone's said to me tonight. I'm [name].", note: "\u2713 Specific observation, warm approach, introduced yourself. They feel seen, not pressured." },
