            good: { user: "I owe you a second impression. The first one was... a draft. Let me buy you coffee and show you the final version.", ai: "*(grinning)* A DRAFT. Okay that's actually the best thing anyone's said to me. Yes.", note: "\u2713 Reframe with humor + initiative. They're charmed by the recovery more than they were put off by the original." },
