            bad: { user: "*(only has friends who are coupled up, feels increasingly isolated)*", ai: "*(you're the odd one out at every gathering now)*", note: "\u274c All eggs in one basket. When the basket changes, you're alone." },
            good: { user: "I've started reaching out to people at different life stages \u2014 some single, some married, some older. My social world feels bigger and less dependent on one group.", ai: "*(that diversity is your safety net)*", note: "\u2713 Diversified. Now no single life change in one friend can make you feel alone." },
