            bad: { user: "I'm fine. I've got my routines. I keep busy.", ai: "*(gently)* Busy isn't the same as connected. How are you really?", note: "\u274c 'Keeping busy' is a cover. Activity without connection is just motion." },
            good: { user: "I'm going to be honest. I'm lonely. I didn't expect retirement to feel this empty. I miss having people around.", ai: "*(warmly)* Thank you for saying that out loud. That takes guts. Let's figure this out together.", note: "\u2713 Named it. The shame releases. Now you can act." },
