            good: { user: "*(walks over to the quietest person)* Hey. I'm hiding from the small talk. Can I hide over here with you?", ai: "*(laughs with relief)* Please. I've been hoping someone would come rescue me.", note: "\u2713 Found your person. Two introverts bonding over mutual social exhaustion is the beginning of a beautiful friendship." },
