            good: { user: "We've hung out a few times and it's getting better each time. Less small talk, more real stuff. I think this one's going to be deep.", ai: "*(the slow build is the whole point. This is how introverts make lifelong friends.)*", note: "\u2713 Trusted the process. The best friendships are slow cookers, not microwaves." },
