            good: { user: "I want to be honest. I've noticed I'm always the one reaching out. It makes me feel like this friendship is more important to me than it is to you. Am I wrong?", ai: "*(their response is the whole answer)*", note: "\u2713 Named it. If they're shocked and apologize, the friendship might be worth saving. If they're defensive or dismissive, you have clarity." },
