            bad: { user: "*(in a meeting)* Actually, that was MY idea. I said it 20 minutes ago.", ai: "*(embarrassed, defensive)* I was just building on the conversation. That's how collaboration works.", note: "\u274c Public callout. Even if you're right, you look petty. They look like a victim." },
            good: { user: "*(pulls them aside after)* Hey, I wanted to mention something. In the meeting, the idea about [X] \u2014 that came from our conversation last week. I'd appreciate the attribution.", ai: "*(caught but not cornered)* You're right. I should have credited you. I'll mention it in the follow-up.", note: "\u2713 Private, direct, specific. They can fix it without losing face." },
