            bad: { user: "*(stays silent when someone else's idea gets stolen too)*", ai: "*(the culture of idea-theft continues)*", note: "\u274c Didn't break the pattern. It'll keep happening." },
            good: { user: "*(in meeting)* I want to build on what Alex brought up last week \u2014 the approach to [X] was really strong.", ai: "*(Alex lights up. Others notice the attribution.)*", note: "\u2713 Modeled the behavior. When you credit others publicly, the culture shifts." },
